  "transcript": {
    "language": "en",
    "is_generated": false,
    "segments": [
      {
        "start": 0.5,
        "duration": 1.1,
        "text": "- Wordsmiths, hello."
      },
      {
        "start": 1.6,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "I've got just one word to\ntalk about in this video,"
      },
      {
        "start": 4.0,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "because it's surprisingly complicated,"
      },
      {
        "start": 6.2,
        "duration": 3.0,
        "text": "and that word is objective."
      },
      {
        "start": 9.3,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "That's my objective for this video,"
      },
      {
        "start": 11.2,
        "duration": 3.3,
        "text": "to describe the word\nobjective objectively."
      },
      {
        "start": 14.5,
        "duration": 1.4,
        "text": "Ugh, we're already in hot water,"
      },
      {
        "start": 15.9,
        "duration": 2.1,
        "text": "and I'm barely 15 seconds in."
      },
      {
        "start": 18.1,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "This word has two different meanings,"
      },
      {
        "start": 19.9,
        "duration": 3.4,
        "text": "one as a noun and one as an adjective."
      },
      {
        "start": 24.4,
        "duration": 3.9,
        "text": "Let's do the noun first.\nAs a noun, it means a goal."
      },
      {
        "start": 28.3,
        "duration": 3.5,
        "text": "It's the thing you want to achieve or do,"
      },
      {
        "start": 31.8,
        "duration": 4.1,
        "text": "but as an adjective, it\nmeans based on facts,"
      },
      {
        "start": 36.0,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "not personal opinions or feelings."
      },
      {
        "start": 40.2,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "So why is this complicated?"
      },
      {
        "start": 42.7,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "We'll come at this from two angles."
      },
      {
        "start": 44.2,
        "duration": 3.1,
        "text": "First, let's do a quick word\norigin on the word object,"
      },
      {
        "start": 47.3,
        "duration": 1.8,
        "text": "which is inside of objective."
      },
      {
        "start": 49.1,
        "duration": 2.8,
        "text": "Comes from two Latin word parts."
      },
      {
        "start": 51.9,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "So we've got the prefix ob,"
      },
      {
        "start": 53.5,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "which means in front of or against,"
      },
      {
        "start": 57.4,
        "duration": 3.8,
        "text": "and ject, which means to throw or place."
      },
      {
        "start": 61.2,
        "duration": 3.1,
        "text": "So in the very most basic\nsense of what an object is,"
      },
      {
        "start": 64.3,
        "duration": 3.5,
        "text": "it's a thing that has been\nplaced in front of you."
      },
      {
        "start": 67.8,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "It's a thing. It's a physical thing."
      },
      {
        "start": 70.0,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "The idea of an object as a goal"
      },
      {
        "start": 71.6,
        "duration": 1.4,
        "text": "eventually developed out of this."
      },
      {
        "start": 73.0,
        "duration": 2.0,
        "text": "An object is a thing in front of you"
      },
      {
        "start": 75.0,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "that you aim at, like a target."
      },
      {
        "start": 77.4,
        "duration": 2.9,
        "text": "That's where you get the\nidea of objective as goal."
      },
      {
        "start": 80.3,
        "duration": 3.5,
        "text": "It's a thing in front of you\nthat you are reaching for."
      },
      {
        "start": 83.8,
        "duration": 2.0,
        "text": "That's objective as a noun."
      },
      {
        "start": 86.8,
        "duration": 2.5,
        "text": "Now, let's discuss\nobjective as an adjective"
      },
      {
        "start": 89.3,
        "duration": 1.5,
        "text": "from another angle."
      },
      {
        "start": 90.9,
        "duration": 3.6,
        "text": "This involves a little\nphilosophy and a little grammar."
      },
      {
        "start": 94.5,
        "duration": 3.5,
        "text": "Fortunately, I know a guy. I am he."
      },
      {
        "start": 98.0,
        "duration": 4.1,
        "text": "So real quick pronoun\nreview, subjects and objects."
      },
      {
